<p>
<lb n="1"/>śakavarṣaṁbulu 1043 <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> ya śrīpritvīvallabhamahā <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="2"/>raka satyāśrayakulati<unclear>laka cālukyābharaṇa śrīmattri</unclear>bhuvanamalladēvara pravarddhamānavijayarājyamuttamōtta
<lb n="3" break="no"/>rābhivṛddhigā śrīmacālukyavikramasaṁvatsa 45 gu śrāhi guddavādināṇṭi peddaḍāka<supplied reason="omitted">rē</supplied>mi śrībhīmēsvaramahādēvara
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ku dakṣiṇayanasaṁkrāṁttinimittāna yi yūri mā<unclear>ni</unclear>munnūṭi sāni gāmāsuggala kūṁttuṟu gomari śrībhīmēsva
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ramahādēvarakuṁ beṭṭina Akhaṇḍavartti lōhada<unclear>ṇḍu di</unclear>viya 1 <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> dīniki nācaṁdrārkkāmu neyi sariyiṁccuvārugā śrī
<lb n="6" break="no"/>bhīmēsvaramahādēvara kilaramuna nāvabōla <unclear>prō</unclear>layayuṁ gāṭabōla paṇḍayayu neṟiyabhōla bādayayu
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ṁ dalarāsi nāvaya bberasina bōlu nalvuruṁ bū<unclear>ṇṭa</unclear>gā neṟiyabōla bādani yaḍapuna kannabōla nūṁkani vasa
<lb n="8" break="no"/>muna viḍicina yinpaEḍlu 50 <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> dīniki nityapaḍigāṁ go<unclear>la</unclear>vaṁgala tribhuvanāṁkuśamuna nēti māna 1 <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> li<supplied reason="omitted">khi</supplied>taṁ peddanācari <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
